fields.name: Eternal Love Rose Bouquet
fields.description: A stunning arrangement of velvety red and delicate pink roses, symbolizing eternal love and passion. This bouquet is perfect for expressing deep emotions and romantic sentiments.

fields.name: Sunset Tulip Medley
fields.description: A vibrant burst of tulips in warm sunset hues, ranging from deep orange and golden yellow to soft pink. This bouquet captures the essence of a picturesque sunset, radiating energy and optimism.

fields.name: Lily Serenity Bouquet
fields.description: An elegant assortment of pure white lilies, exuding serenity and grace. This bouquet invokes a sense of calm and purity, making it an ideal choice for weddings and peaceful occasions.

fields.name: Radiant Sunflower Harmony
fields.description: A cheerful arrangement featuring bright sunflowers, symbolizing adoration and loyalty. Accented with lush greenery, this bouquet radiates warmth and happiness, bringing a touch of sunshine to any setting.

fields.name: Daisy Dreams Blossom
fields.description: A playful bouquet adorned with cheerful daisies in various colors, evoking feelings of innocence and joy. This whimsical arrangement is perfect for celebrations and moments of pure delight.

fields.name: Orchid Elegance Ensemble
fields.description: An exotic display of orchids in shades of purple, pink, and white, exuding elegance and sophistication. This bouquet showcases the beauty of orchids, making it a luxurious and stylish choice for special events.

fields.name: Carnation Carnival Bliss
fields.description: A vibrant medley of carnations in bold and lively colors, representing love and fascination. This lively bouquet captures the spirit of a carnival, adding a playful and colorful touch to any occasion.

fields.name: Chrysanthemum Jubilee Delight
fields.description: A festive arrangement featuring chrysanthemums in rich autumn hues, symbolizing joy and celebration. With its warm colors and cheerful vibe, this bouquet is perfect for festive gatherings and harvest-themed events.

fields.name: Hydrangea Whispers Bouquet
fields.description: A dreamy bouquet showcasing delicate hydrangea blooms in shades of blue, pink, and lavender. This bouquet whispers of romance and enchantment, making it an enchanting choice for weddings and romantic gestures.
